    <rigor-hint>FULL</rigor-hint>
    <rigor-reason>Production code change in `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/AnalysisContextBuilder.cs`; affects LLM context window correctness (drops messages, reorders pairs); FULL rigor + Step 9.5 quality gates mandatory</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>P2-W2</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>true</parallel-safe>
    <parallel-reason>Disjoint file (`AnalysisContextBuilder.cs` in `Services/Ai/`) vs task 023 (`AnalysisChatContextResolver.cs` in `Services/Ai/Chat/`) — different files within the Ai module. Parallel-safe with task 023 if both run in Wave 1. Conservatively placed in Wave 2 in case 023 escalates to factory edits.</parallel-reason>
